OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain across northern Scotland
OL,6,Fwill be slow to clear. Elsewhere
OL,7,Fsunshine and showers, these heaviest
OL,8,Fand most frequent across western
OL,9,Fareas, while parts of the east may
OL,10,Fremain dry. Temperatures still a
OL,11,Flittle on the cool side.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers continuing across
OL,14,Fsome western areas, perhaps merging
OL,15,Finto a longer spell of rain across
OL,16,Fparts of the southwest. Many central
OL,17,Fand northern areas becoming dry and
OL,18,Fchilly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
