OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FSunshine and showers for many,
OL,6,Falthough parts of the north may remain
OL,7,Fdry. More persistent rain moves into
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland, Wales and southwest
OL,9,FEngland by evening. Temperatures
OL,10,Faround average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
